+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+<br>
|                                                                             |<br>
|                  Welcome to Legacy's Dawning - Help!                      |<br>
|                                                                             |<br>
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+<br>
<br>
The following commands will help you along your journeys, whether you are a new<br>
player or a seasoned veteran.<br>
<br>
     Index             : List all help file categories<br>
     Help [subject]    : Display help file on a given subject<br>
     Command           : List all command categories<br>
     Command [subject] : Display all commands within a given category<br>
     Options           : Display/Change your character's option flags<br>
     Iflag             : Display/Change system and noteboard information<br>
     Message           : Display/Change operational messages displayed to you<br>
     Color             : Set your terminal type and color preferences<br>
     Score             : See your character's statistics<br>
     Identity {id}     : See your character's appearance information<br>
     Inventory {inv}   : See what items your character is holding<br>
<br>
Recommended reading:<br>
<br>
     Help newbie       : Information pointers for new players<br>
     Help pray         : Information about dieties and their assistance<br>
     Help syntax       : How commands are structured for this system<br>
<br>
If you cannot find a particular help file by name, browse the index listings.<br>
If all else fails, contact an immortal by typing 'request imm need help please'<br>
<br>
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+<br>
